msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.616:0.2"
msgid "11. Rāgapeyyāla "
msgstr "11. Abbreviated Texts Beginning With Greed "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.616:0.3"
msgid "616 "
msgstr "616 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an7.616:1.1"
msgid "“Rāgassa, bhikkhave, abhiññāya satta dhammā bhāvetabbā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, for insight into greed, seven things should be developed. "

msgctxt "an7.616:1.2"
msgid "Katame satta? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "an7.616:1.3"
msgid "Aniccasaññā, anattasaññā, asubhasaññā, ādīnavasaññā, pahānasaññā, virāgasaññā, nirodhasaññā—"
msgstr "The perception of impermanence, the perception of not-self, the perception of ugliness, the perception of drawbacks, the perception of giving up, the perception of fading away, and the perception of cessation. "

msgctxt "an7.616:1.4"
msgid "rāgassa, bhikkhave, abhiññāya ime satta dhammā bhāvetabbā”ti. "
msgstr "These seven things should be developed for insight into greed.”"

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
